<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <title>Welcome to <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f6fb;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      font-family: 'Manrope', "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    table {
      border-spacing: 0;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f3f6fb;
      padding: 24px 12px;
    }
    .card {
      border: 2px solid #00296b;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 640px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header-image {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 36px 42px 24px;
      color: #292929;
    }
    .heading {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-family: Manrope, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 120%;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      color: #292929;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .body {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-family: Manrope, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 120%;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      color: #292929;
    }
    .button-wrap {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 0 16px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #00296b;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: Manrope, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 120%;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 0 42px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: Manrope, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 140%;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #6c7480;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }

    .flex {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
      .content,
      .footer {
        padding-left: 20px !important;
        padding-right: 20px !important;
      }
      .heading {
        font-size: 20px !important;
      }
      .body {
        font-size: 16px !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" class="wrapper">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" class="card" width="640">
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dpi44zxlw/image/upload/v1772611742/header_hjx0ag.png"
                alt="<%= appName %>"
                class="header-image"
              >
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="content">
              <h1 class="heading">Welcome to <%= appName %>!</h1>
              <p class="body">Hi <%= fullName %>,</p>
              <p class="body">Welcome to <%= appName %></p>
              <p class="body">We're excited to help you secure financial support for your tuition  quickly, transparently, and without hidden fees.</p>
              <p class="body">Here's what you can do next:</p>
              <p class="body">✔ Complete your profile</p>
              <p class="body">✔ Check your funding eligibility</p>
              <p class="body">✔ Submit your first funding request</p>
              <p class="body">Funding is disbursed directly to your school after verification, ensuring peace of mind for you and your institution.</p>
              <p class="body">Ready to begin?</p>
              <div class="button-wrap">
                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Complete Your Profile</a>
              </div>
              
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="">
              <p class="heading" style="color: #001d4c; font-weight: 600;">© PAYMYFEES.CO <%= new Date().getFullYear() %>.</p>
              <p class="flex">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dpi44zxlw/image/upload/v1772623805/Frame_1618869201_no2yks.png" alt="facebook" />
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dpi44zxlw/image/upload/v1772623805/Frame_1618869202_yi6oh9.png" alt="instagram" />
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dpi44zxlw/image/upload/v1772623805/Frame_1618869203_kbutsh.png" alt="linkedIn" />
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>